gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 123, Wizards 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Wizards, 123-112. Klay Thompson led the Warriors with 25 points, three rebounds, and four assists as Jonathan Kuminga added 21 points, six rebounds, and five assists. Kyle Kuzma led the Wizards with 27 points and 12 rebounds. The Warriors move to 30-27 on the year (4-1 over their last five since Klay Thompson moved to bench) while the Wizards move to 9-49.
